.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Amplify outputs.
# /amplify_outputs.json is committed because Angular needs it at build time and
# it only contains client-public IDs (Cognito user pool, AppSync endpoint, API
# key). These are visible in any browser DevTools — they're not secrets. The
# server-side polla-backend repo's amplify_outputs.json stays gitignored.
src/amplify_outputs.json
